window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b><p>Once a thief, always a thief...and he's just walked away with her heart. </p></b> <p><b></b>Ex-military security specialist Luke Phillips would like nothing more than to walk away from his latest job, especially when he realizes the upscale market owner is the daughter of the man responsible for his year spent in juvie. </p> <p>Except he promised the kids at the community center new and updated equipment. He has no choice but to keep to himself and try not to get mixed up with Emery Vincent. No matter how sweet and sexy she is.One look at Luke starts Emery's heart fluttering - along with other specific body parts. But she knows better than to act on those urges with a bad boy who looks at her like he's been living off rations and she's the market's hot lunch special.But when he rescues her and bandages up her scuffed knee, the heat between them explodes. While a future between them is impossible, hot, sweaty sex is guaranteed - at least until the job is done. Unless Luke can let go of the past and risk it all for love. </p> <p><b>Warning:</b> This book contains a smoking-hot-ex-convict from the wrong side of the tracks, and a silver-spoon lady who gets oh, so much more than she bargained for when she hires him for a job. </p>"; 
